CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 6, 1960, pg. A9 reads: "On The Patio - Three of the Frogs got together with some of the out-of-town guests on the patio of the beautiful new home of the William Fredericks in Oakmont, where the Frogs hosted a breakfast following the formal. Left to right: Frog Dr. Robert Bolden, Mrs. Alice Trigg of Washington, D.C.; Mrs. Donald Watson and Mr. Watson, Cleveland, Ohio; Mrs. William Jackson and Mr. Jackson, East Pittsburgh; Mrs. Calvin Crawford and Mr. Crawford, Dayton, Ohio; Mrs. Charles Holt and Dr. Holt, Pittsburgh, and Frogs Dr. C.C. Blow and Percy A. Garland. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Dr. Robert Bolden, Alice Trigg, Mr. and Mrs. Donald Watson, Mr. and Mrs. William Jackson, Mr. and Mrs. Calvin Crawford, Mr. and Mrs. Charles Holt, Dr. C. C. Blow, and Percy A. Garland, posed on patio at home of Mr. and Mrs. William Frederick, for breakfast party after FROGS formal, Oakmont
